| Feature            | MERN                                     | .NET                                                  |
| ------------------ | ---------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| **Language**       | JavaScript (full-stack)                  | C# (main)                                             |
| **Primary Use**    | Web apps, SPAs, startups, real-time apps | Enterprise apps, banking, healthcare, large systems   |
| **Database**       | MongoDB (NoSQL)                          | SQL Server, PostgreSQL, MySQL                         |
| **Performance**    | Great for I/O-heavy apps, scalable       | Excellent for CPU-intensive, enterprise-scale apps    |
| **Learning Curve** | Easy if familiar with JS                 | Steeper, requires knowledge of C# and Microsoft tools |
| **Cost**           | Mostly free, open-source                 | Free with .NET Core, enterprise tools may incur cost  |
| **Community**      | Large open-source community              | Strong enterprise & Microsoft support                 |
